====Hyponyms====
* {{sense|genus}} {{taxlink|Xenophora conchyliophora|species}} ({{vern|American carriersnail|pedia=1}}&nbsp;- [[type species]]); {{taxlink|Xenophora cerea|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora chinensis|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora corrugata|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora crispa|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora flindersi|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora granulosa|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora indica|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora japonica|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora mekranensis|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora minuta|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora neozelanica|species}} ({{vern|New Zealand carriershell|pedia=1}}), {{taxlink|Xenophora pallidula|species}} ({{vern|pallid carrier shell|pedia=1}}), {{taxlink|Xenophora peroniana|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora robusta|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora senegalensis|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora solarioides|species}}, {{taxlink|Xenophora tenuis|species}} {{qualifier|species}}
