#* {{quote-newsgroup|en|author=Henk Senster|title=I would like to know|newsgroup=pl.soc.polityka|url=https://groups.google.com/g/pl.soc.polityka/c/xc_DnPGp9K8/m/BpZNRJ0kv4QJ|accessdate=2022-06-08|date=Feb 10, 2003|passage=Another one in this thread called us the most racial mixed nation of the world cause he saw three or four coloured players in our national footballteam. And you call us '''xenofobes''' probably cause I was a little to disappointed and sarcastically about the support of the Polish Government for the USA and against the 'old Europe'. Ce que la vérité?}}
