=====Usage notes=====
* ''Xanh lá cây'' or ''xanh lục'' become clunky when overused. Most of the time, simply ''xanh'' is clear enough, and {{m|vi|lục}} and {{m|vi|lam}} can be used when necessary avoid confusion.
