==Maltese==
===Etymology===
From {{m|mt|x'}} + earlier {{m|mt||*iex|t=what}}, of which latter {{m|mt|x'}} is itself a contraction, thus a reduplicative formation. {{m|mt||*Iex}} is from {{der|mt|ar|[[أَيُّ]] [[شَيْء]]|lit=what thing}}, exactly equivalent to {{cog|ary|آش|tr=ʔāš}}. Also cognate with {{cog|acw|إيش|tr=ēš}}, where the contracted vowel is different, however.
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|mt|/ʃɪːʃ/}}
===Pronoun===
{{head|mt|pronoun}}
# {{lb|mt|interrogative}} [[what]]
====Usage notes====
* Used following a verb or preposition and in isolation. For details on usage, see the notes at {{m|mt|x'}}.
====See also====
* {{l|mt|x'}}
* {{l|mt|x'inhu}}

