From {{confix|en|xeno|phobe}}. From {{uder|en|grc|ξένος||foreign, strange}}, + {{uder|en|grc|φόβος||fear}}.
===Pronunciation===
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|en|/ˈzɛ.nə.foʊb/|/ˈzi.nə.foʊb/}}
* {{a|RP}} {{IPA|en|/ˈzɛ.nə.fəʊb/}}
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# One who [[hate]]s or [[fear]]s [[stranger]]s or [[foreigner]]s.
====Synonyms====
* {{l|en|xenophobiac}} {{q|rare}}
* {{l|en|xenophobian}} {{q|rare}}
* {{l|en|xenophobic}}
* {{l|en|xenophobist}}
* See also [[Thesaurus:xenophobe]]
====Antonyms====
* {{l|en|xenophile}}
====Related terms====
{{rel4|en
|xenophobia
|xenophobic
|xenophobical
|xenophobically
}}
